divs: Sighting DetailsSighting Report: I took digital pictures near Austin on Sunday January 23, 2005. When I looked at the pictures later one of them had a small object which looks like a UFO. I did not see anything at the time. The pictures right before and after showed nothing. Give me an email address to send the digital pictures for analysis. I have a local friend you can also contact David Harrienger in Austin, Texas (512) 394-0714 gran899@flash.net
